org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common

Class UniversalSchedulerListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.UniversalSchedulerListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, SchedulerEventListener

    public class UniversalSchedulerListener
extends Object
implements SchedulerEventListener, Serializable
    Wrapper class for Scheduler Event Listener. The goal of this class is to overcome the classloading problem (i.e. the user defined scheduler listener stub have to be loaded on Scheduler core side).
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 2.1
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

      Invoked each time a scheduler event occurs.

      void taskStateUpdatedEvent(NotificationData<TaskInfo> notification)
      Invoked each time the state of a task has changed.
